  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, mix together Turkish Delight, Greek Yogurt, ground almonds, honey, flax seeds, vanilla extract, and beaten eggs. Add granulated sugar and stir well.",
    "Transfer the mixture to an ovenproof dish or pan that has been lightly greased with oil or butter.",
    "Bake at 180°C (350°F) for about 25-30 minutes until golden brown on top and set in the center.",
    "Let it cool slightly before serving. Garnish with additional honey if desired."
